---
import { getEntry } from 'astro:content'

const { data: author } = await getEntry('authors', 'NPMRUN')
---

<style lang="scss" is:global>
    .copyright {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        margin: 15px 0;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-left: 3px solid #007bff;

        h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;

            &:hover {
                color: #0056b3;
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="copyright">
    <h3>版权声明</h3>
    <p>
        本博客所有文章均为原创内容，版权归原作者所有。未经作者允许，禁止转载、摘编、复制或建立镜像。
    </p>
    <p>如需转载，请通过以下方式联系作者：</p>
    <p><a href={'mailto:' + author.email}>{author.email}</a></p>
</div>
